@startuml
!include ../../style.puml

title tick() Makes Progress Explicit

participant "Test" as Test
participant "Simulator" as Sim
box "Cluster" #E6F3FF
participant "athens" as Athens
participant "byzantium" as Byzantium
participant "cyrene" as Cyrene
end box
participant "Client History" as History

Test -> Sim : tick()
Sim -> Athens : accept client write
Sim -> History : record invocation
Test -> Sim : assert write started

Test -> Sim : tick()
Sim -> Byzantium : deliver replicate write
Sim -> Cyrene : drop / delay replicate write
Test -> Sim : assert one replica has progressed

Test -> Sim : tick()
Sim -> Athens : deliver follower ack
Sim -> Athens : mark quorum reached
Sim -> History : record success response
Test -> Sim : assert client-visible outcome

note across #E6F3FF
Same inputs plus the same tick sequence
produce the same execution trace.
end note

@enduml
